	<language>en_US</language>
	<keyword>isdir</keyword>
	<short_description
  >Returns true is the input argument is an directory.</short_description>

	<syntax>
		<syntax_item>r = isdir(dirname)</syntax_item>
	</syntax>
	
	<param_input>
		<param_input_item>
			<param_name>dirname</param_name>
			<param_description>a string: directory name to check.</param_description>
		</param_input_item>
	</param_input>

	<param_output>

		<param_output_item>
			<param_name>r</param_name>
			<param_description>a logical: true if it is an directory.</param_description>
		</param_output_item>

	</param_output>

	<description>
<p><b>isdir(dirname)</b> returns <b>true</b> if <b
      >dirname</b> is a directory.</p>
<p><b>isdir</b> and <b>isfolder</b> are same.</p>
</description>


